			<task><p>Where is the triangle created by the angle <m>210^\circ</m>?</p></task>
		</task>
		<task>
			<introduction><p>Angles of measure <m>45^\circ</m> and <m>315^\circ</m></p></introduction>
			<task><p>What is the sine value for both points?</p></task>
			<task><p>Compare the sine values for these two points.</p></task>
			<task><p>Where is the triangle created by the angle <m>315^\circ</m>?</p></task>
		</task>
		<task>
			<introduction><p>Angles of measure <m>45^\circ</m> and <m>405^\circ</m></p></introduction>
			<task><p>Compare the sine values for these two points.</p></task>
